channel.title: Editing Names/Server Name
channel.description: Hey everyone i need help editing my server characters. Most of the Owner commands are set to the original makers name and when i try to change them to my name nothing happens. The commands still only work for the original maker. Ex: ::hail, ::alltome, ::givetitle, and other owner commands. I made myself owner rank aswell (im not that stupid). Also i cant change the names under the mod/admin/owner list to my staff there stuck at what the original creator made them. -Any help is appreciated. -thanks!
